Class SimpleEvolutionaryAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amihaiemil.eva.SimpleEvolutionaryAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Eva

    public final class SimpleEvolutionaryAlgorithm
extends Object
implements Eva
    Simple evolutionary algorithm implementation. No threads, special stopping conditions or error range. This class is immutable and thread safe.
    Author:
    Mihai Andronache (amihaiemil@gmail.com)
